name: name
description: User friendly name of the asset

name: assetId
description: Unique string id to identify your asset

name: priority
description: Defines a priority in which the assets of a form template will added in the form visualizer page

name: resourceType
description: The kind of the asset (FONT or CSS)

name: inputType
description: The type of storage where the asset is saved, can be only URL or FILE

name: file
description: Contains the information of a file uploaded with the file service.

name: url
description: The url of an external asset that the form visualizer will load

name: fontFamily
description: The font-family of the uploaded font.

name: fontFormat
description: the @font-face src format of the uploaded font
